      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，DiagnosticEngine是核心引擎，HIPAA_Vault是合规存储。您提到的是两个独立节点，还是需要把Vault放到一个子图里？",
      "elements_involved": [
